messages.message: Hi do we have an idea when this will be fixed? I have a customer deadline by mid day UK time, and i’m currently blocked on this error

Hey, the actual fix still needs to be implemented, and we just missed today's release-certify for next Tuesday's prod push. I think most likely the fix will be on instabase.com (http://instabase.com) by the following Tuesday (Sep 12)

cc @Sławek Biel @Rafal @pauline.comising
@lydia once it’s implemented & verified on ib.com (http://ib.com), can we get that pushed to sandboxes?  The key error is still present on my sandbox, it just happens less frequently

It'll be part of a patch release of 23.07, which can be applied to sandboxes. I don't know who manages the sandbox you're working with. Some are managed by prod-eng and some are by whoever created it in the first place.
